        "type": "residence",
        "occupants": [
            "emily",
            "haley"
        ],
        "basicDescription": "2 Willow Lane is the home of sisters Emily and Haley. It's located along the southern road in Pelican Town, just next to 1 Willow Lane where Jodi, Kent and their sons live.",
